---
// Purpose-Built Capabilities section for Trade & Field Services industry page
---

<section id="capabilities" class="cre-capabilities-section">
  <div class="cre-capabilities-container">
    <span class="section-label">PURPOSE-BUILT CAPABILITIES</span>
    <h2 class="cre-capabilities-headline">
      Field service systems engineered for your workflow
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-capabilities-grid">
      <!-- Job Dispatch & Scheduling -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-1.webp" alt="Job Dispatch & Scheduling" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Job Dispatch & Scheduling</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Intelligent job dispatch that automatically routes jobs to available technicians based on skills, location, and capacity. Optimizes travel routes, reduces wasted time, and ensures fastest response to customer requests.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Automated job-to-technician matching</li>
            <li>Route optimization and mapping</li>
            <li>Real-time availability tracking</li>
            <li>Technician skill-based assignment</li>
            <li>Customer request prioritization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mobile Job Management -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-5.webp" alt="Mobile Job Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Mobile Job Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Mobile-first platform that gives technicians job details, customer history, and required parts on arrival. Technicians capture photos, notes, and time without returning to office, enabling real-time accuracy and visibility.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Job details and customer history on-site</li>
            <li>Photo and documentation capture</li>
            <li>Real-time time and material tracking</li>
            <li>Signature and approval capture</li>
            <li>Mobile invoice generation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Customer Communication & Updates -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-6.webp" alt="Customer Communication & Updates" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Customer Communication & Updates</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified customer communication that sends appointment confirmations, real-time arrival alerts, job completion notifications, and payment reminders. Reduces no-shows and improves customer experience.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Appointment confirmations and reminders</li>
            <li>Arrival time notifications</li>
            <li>Job progress updates to customer</li>
            <li>Work completion confirmations</li>
            <li>Automated payment reminders</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Time & Material Tracking -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-2.webp" alt="Time & Material Tracking" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Time & Material Tracking</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time capture of labor time, parts used, and materials consumed on every job. Provides instant visibility into job profitability and enables accurate invoicing without re-entry.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>On-site time capture</li>
            <li>Parts and material usage tracking</li>
            <li>Equipment and tool logging</li>
            <li>Labor cost by job and technician</li>
            <li>Material cost reconciliation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Inventory & Parts Management -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-3.webp" alt="Inventory & Parts Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Inventory & Parts Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time inventory tracking that surfaces part availability to dispatchers before assigning jobs. Prevents technicians from arriving at jobs without needed parts, reducing callbacks and improving first-time fix rates.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Real-time part availability</li>
            <li>Parts forecasting and ordering</li>
            <li>Truck inventory management</li>
            <li>Parts usage analytics</li>
            <li>Supplier integration and tracking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Billing & Performance Analytics -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-7.webp" alt="Billing & Performance Analytics" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Billing & Performance Analytics</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated billing that generates invoices from tracked time and materials without manual work. Real-time profitability tracking shows which jobs, technicians, and service types deliver best margins.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Automated invoice generation</li>
            <li>Service quality tracking</li>
            <li>First-time fix rate analytics</li>
            <li>Technician productivity metrics</li>
            <li>Job profitability by type and location</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-capabilities-section {
    background: #0052CC;
    color: #ffffff;
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capability-card {
    background: transparent;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .cre-capability-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .cre-capability-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-section {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .cre-includes-section strong {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-includes-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li::before {
    content: "â€¢";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-capabilities-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-capability-card {
      padding: 28px 20px;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .cre-capability-title {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cre-capability-description {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cre-includes-list li {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>


